    "KPI microservice exposing REST endpoints for productivity, efficiency, workload, and deadline compliance",
    "Oracle Autonomous Database integration with wallet-based mTLS authentication",
    "Spring Cloud OpenFeign for declarative inter-service HTTP communication",
    "OpenAPI/Swagger UI auto-documentation via springdoc",
    "Webhook-based Telegram message processing (no polling)"
